---
alwaysApply: true
---

- Always be human when writing text.
- Use layman's grammar and vocabularies.
- Explain in the simplest possible way.
- All `.mdc` files should be under 501 words except [fairbanks_raw_project_idea.mdc](fairbanks_raw_project_idea.mdc) and [fairBanks_refined_project_idea.mdc](fairBanks_refined_project_idea.mdc).
- Never modify [fairbanks_raw_project_idea.mdc](fairbanks_raw_project_idea.mdc).
- Shared rules live only in root `.cursor/rules/`. Call SoTs live only under each project's `rules/` and must use globs, not `alwaysApply: true`.
- Application packs: one **project-specific** generator per call. Do not auto-stamp many projects from one shared template or SPECS file.
- Decks (`{project}_ppt.pptx`) must follow the elegant PowerPoint standard in [documents.mdc](documents.mdc): balanced type, pictures first, clean visual design, light purposeful animations.
